01:49.610 --> 01:50.890
LORI:
Potsie.

01:50.890 --> 01:51.980
Yeah?

01:51.980 --> 01:53.480
Mr. Higgins really
liked the chart.

01:53.980 --> 01:55.980
He especially liked the way
you followed the jujube

01:55.980 --> 01:57.980
all the way through
the large intestine.

01:58.490 --> 01:58.990
(chuckles)

