It was nothing.

02:01.200 --> 02:02.410
LORI:
Say, how are you

02:02.410 --> 02:05.490
at drawing the
reproductive system?

02:05.490 --> 02:06.880
Can't you get arrested
for that?

02:06.880 --> 02:07.960
(Lori chuckles)

02:07.960 --> 02:09.130
LORI:
I know you'll do it

02:09.130 --> 02:10.710
just terrific.

02:10.710 --> 02:12.220
Yeah.

02:12.220 --> 02:13.220
(chuckles)

02:13.220 --> 02:14.220
Are you kissing
my girl?

02:14.220 --> 02:15.220
Oh, no.

02:15.220 --> 02:17.220
Uh, she was just thanking me
for helping her.

02:17.220 --> 02:18.220
Right guys?
RICHIE:
Yeah, right.

02:18.720 --> 02:20.640
Oh, yeah, yeah, he was helping
her with reproduction.

02:20.640 --> 02:22.730
(screams)

02:22.730 --> 02:24.230
Well, I-I meant
biology.

02:24.230 --> 02:25.730
You're dead.
Careful, this is
my lucky shirt.

02:25.730 --> 02:28.230
Bernie.

02:28.230 --> 02:29.680
Hey, will you tell him
that he's innocent?

02:29.680 --> 02:31.650
I don't want to
get involved.

02:31.650 --> 02:34.240
All right, come on, listen,
it's-it's no problem, really.

02:34.240 --> 02:35.020
He's just...

02:39.360 --> 02:41.360
I just hope for your sake that
you're helping my good friend

02:41.860 --> 02:43.700
up to his feet here.

02:43.700 --> 02:44.830
Who are you?

02:44.830 --> 02:47.250
Hey, what are you,
from out of town?

02:48.590 --> 02:51.090
I'm taking him outside
to bust his head in,

02:51.090 --> 02:52.540
unless you want to go
in his place, big mouth.

02:55.010 --> 02:57.010
Big mouth?

02:57.010 --> 02:58.510
All right, look, look,
it's all a misunderstanding.

02:58.510 --> 03:00.010
He was just trying
to help your girl

03:00.010 --> 03:01.800
with homework,
and that's all.

03:01.800 --> 03:03.350
Is that true?

03:03.350 --> 03:05.390
Yes.

03:05.390 --> 03:06.890
Why didn't you say so?

03:06.890 --> 03:07.890
(hoarse):
I tried.

03:07.890 --> 03:09.390
What's the matter
with your voice?

03:09.890 --> 03:10.390
(hoarse):
I'm scared.

03:12.890 --> 03:13.890
Hey, uh, Bernard.

03:13.890 --> 03:15.200
Bernie.

03:15.200 --> 03:16.280
Oh, I'm sorry.

03:16.280 --> 03:19.780
Bernard, I thought that we
had a rendezvous outside.

03:19.780 --> 03:20.780
It's settled, Fonz.

03:20.780 --> 03:22.290
Hey, I'll tell you
when it's settled.

03:22.290 --> 03:23.570
Let's go, Bernie.

03:23.570 --> 03:25.150
Hey, what are we fighting for?

03:25.150 --> 03:26.660
We don't even know each other.

03:26.660 --> 03:27.740
Hey, you know me.

03:27.740 --> 03:28.740
I'm big mouth!

03:28.740 --> 03:29.740
But it's a mistake.

03:29.740 --> 03:31.240
Hey, I heard "big mouth"
loud and clear,

03:31.240 --> 03:33.160
and now, Mr. Tourist, I am gonna

03:33.160 --> 03:35.470
show you the parking
lot upside down!

03:35.470 --> 03:37.250
Come on, everybody,
we're gonna see a fight!

03:37.250 --> 03:38.840
(cheering)

03:41.340 --> 03:42.840
Come on, come on!

03:42.840 --> 03:44.840
Come on, Fonz!

